    "content": "<div class=\"noinclude\"><span class=\"breadcrumbs xulRefAttr_breadcrumbs\">Â« <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL/XUL_Reference\">XUL Reference home</a></span></div>\n\n<dl>\n <dt><code id=\"a-attribute\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/attribute\">attribute</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Type: <em>attribute name</em></dd>\n <dd>The attribute that the observer is observing. When the value of the attribute changes, the broadcast event is called on the observer. Use the value <code>*</code> to observe all attribute of the broadcasters. The <code id=\"a-id\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/id\">id</a></code>, <code id=\"a-ref\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/ref\">ref</a></code>, and <code id=\"a-persist\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/persist\">persist</a></code> attributes are not observed.</dd>\n</dl>",
